ADMIN_CMD_KICK: You have been removed from this session by an administrator. Try again later.
ADMIN_CMD_MSG: An administrator has sent you a message.
ADMIN_CMD_NORMAL: An administrator has sent a command to your game.

AR_OBJECTIVE_DESC: Places a beacon at your objective.
AR_WAYPOINT_DESC: Places a beacon at your waypoint.
BATTLEYE_SERVER_DESC:
Runs a real BattlEye server on your client when you are the host.
This will flag modders and might help avoid untrusted host errors

Kicks the player with a BattlEye update message.
The player must restart the game to be able to go online again

Prevents players from creating CEOs and MCs through the interaction menu.

BLOCK_RID_JOINING_DESCRIPTION:
This will block anyone trying to join, track or remote kick you, including your friends. 
Attention: This can be detected by other modders.
